{"id": 7514, "title": "Ticket #7514: Bugfixes and creature comforts for DataReuse", "description": "<blockquote>\nNow that <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7389\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7389'); return false;\" title=\"Expose Data Reuse to the ClassAd\">#7389</a></span> is merged, even though <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=DataReuse\" title=\"Data Reuse\">DataReuse</a></span> is a hidden feature, I'd like to start testing it on some glideins.\n\n<p>This ticket is the catch-all for minor testing improvements and bugfixes.  At the time of writing, this includes:\n\n</p><p></p><ol>\n<li>Any state management bug codefixes.\n</li><li>Improving logging and debugability of the state calculations.\n</li><li>Including statistics into the slot ad for Ganglia integration.  Miron has been asking for metrics on this!</li></ol>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2020-May-02 14:51:43 by bbockelm:</em> <br/>\n\nThis is intended to be an internal feature for this release.  Resolving for now.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2020-Mar-06 22:36</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/576a6391ee8a6b5fc2439d7122df90971c4381c5\">[59097]</a></span>: Publish simple data reuse statistics into the slot ad. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7514\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7514'); return false;\" title=\"Bugfixes and creature comforts for DataReuse\">#7514</a></span>  (By Brian Bockelman )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">202